data.description: Welcome to 106 Vauhan Ct in Jacksonville. Upon entering the home you are met with tons of natural lighting, an open concept with tile floors. Throughout the home you will find carpet in the 3 bedrooms. The primary bedroom hosts a bathroom and walk-in closets. The additional bedrooms also have walk in closet. The outside features a deck, a storage shed and fully fenced back yard, a nice oasis for your four leg friends. Call for your private showing!
